nStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"我们虽然是PasPale，但却并没有创作\n和PasPale有关的东西。用别人创作的东西的集合体\n来展现PasPale，是不是很不可思议？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev73-ep4-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"不过，我觉得这正是偶像帅气的地方！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev73-ep4-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"为什么？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev73-ep4-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"我觉得偶像就是以别人创作的东西为载体，通过\n表演展示，让这些东西超出创作者和观众的想像！\n这一点真的是非常帅气呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev73-ep4-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"千圣","body":"确实，能把别人给予的东西表现得更为出彩，\n这或许就是偶像的专业性呢。不仅仅是歌曲，\n我觉得电视剧和综艺节目也是如此","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"ev73-ep4-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻弥","body":"戏剧也是一种对已有的作品进行进一步诠释的艺术形式。\n思考自己在其中应该怎样表现，\n也是很有趣的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev73-ep4-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"原来如此。我们偶像就是这样的人啊。\n小伊芙也这么觉得吗？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev73-ep4-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"我听了刚才大家的话，有种豁然开朗的感觉。\n模特的工作也是一样的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev73-ep4-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDi